DEG Platform Integration Team

The DEG platform Integration team announces the release of 2016 WW43 Purley-FPGA Server SKX/LBG B-Stepping Silver release package for Intel internal use. The release is based on OS of\n \n Linux\n server. The auto-installer packages are available on the Artifactory server (both SH site and OR site). Any questions please contact Bei, Ling.
